@dpsBase = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@authToken = user_token_123

### Buscar documentos por contenido (similitud vectorial)
POST {{dpsBase}}/document-search/by-content
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "query": "requisitos para habilitar un aeródromo",
  "max_documents": 10
}


### Búsqueda mínima (usa max_documents por defecto)
POST {{dpsBase}}/document-search/by-content
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "query": "normativa de seguridad operacional"
}
